OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,FBritish-based animal lovers have been
OL,8,Fwarned that new EU travel rules have
OL,9,Fmade most pet passports invalid.
OL,11,FAnyone travelling into the EU with pet
OL,12,Fdogs, cats and ferrets will need new
OL,13,Fdocuments and should no longer use EU
OL,14,Fpet passports, under the rules which
OL,15,Fcome into force on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
