OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,FThe GOV.UK website, which says the
OL,8,Frules also apply to assistance dogs,
OL,9,Fstates: "If you live in England,
OL,10,FScotland or Wales, from 22 April you
OL,11,Fcannot use a pet passport (even if it
OL,12,Fwas issued in the EU).
OL,14,F"If you use a pet passport, your pet
OL,15,Fmay be refused entry into the EU."
