OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,FThe changes mean that anyone
OL,8,Ftravelling from Great Britain to an EU
OL,9,Fcountry with a pet will now need to
OL,10,Fget an animal health certificate (AHC)
OL,11,Fbefore they set off.
OL,13,FTravellers will need to get a vet to
OL,14,Fissue an AHC within ten days of their
OL,15,Ftrip.
OL,17,FA new certificate will be needed for
OL,18,Feach trip to the EU.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
