CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776816171
OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,FThe AHC can be used for up to six
OL,8,Fmonths for onward travel within the EU
OL,9,Fand for reentering Britain, as long
OL,10,Fas rabies vaccinations are still valid.
OL,12,FThe Animal and Plant Health Agency
OL,13,F(APHA) said "holidays with your pets
OL,14,Fare still possible" despite the new EU
OL,15,Frules changes.
OL,17,FAn APHA spokesman said: "Anyone
OL,18,Fplanning to travel should check
OL,19,Fguidance on GOV.UK, and the entry
OL,20,Frules for their destination.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
