OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,F"To avoid delays and ensure a smooth
OL,8,Fjourney, pet owners residing in Great
OL,9,FBritain should get an Animal Health
OL,10,FCertificate if they are travelling
OL,11,Ffrom Great Britain to an EU country."
OL,13,FUnder the new rules, EU pet passports
OL,14,Fare now only to be issued to people
OL,15,Fwhose main base is in the EU and not
OL,16,Fto holiday home owners or seasonal
OL,17,Fvisitors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
