OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776816171
OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,FThe Department for Environment, Food
OL,8,Fand Rural Affairs said individual
OL,9,Fmember states may have specific pet
OL,10,Ftravel requirements and owners should
OL,11,Falways check the entry details before
OL,12,Ftravelling.
OL,14,FBritish-based travellers can still use
OL,15,FEU pet passports for their return
OL,16,Fjourney back home.
OL,18,FThe government is updating its
OL,19,Fguidance to pet owners in light of the
OL,20,Fnew EU regulations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
