OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776816171
OL,3,CNo more pet passports: What are the
OL,4,Cnew EU rules for travelling with
OL,5,Canimals?
OL,7,FExtra paperwork will also be needed if
OL,8,Fthe owner is not travelling with their
OL,9,Fpet.
OL,11,FWhoever is taking the animal abroad
OL,12,Fmust have written permission from the
OL,13,Fowner.
OL,15,FUp to five days are allowed before the
OL,16,Fpet and owner must travel abroad.
OL,18,FTravellers are now also only allowed
OL,19,Fto have a maximum of five pets in a
OL,20,Fprivate vehicle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
